{"TopicId":135565,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"KSP land record 2","CreatedByName":"corporelax","CreatedById":136704,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-31T20:53:43Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"corporelax","CreatedById":136704,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-31T20:53:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs the title says but there are rules\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. No physics mods/add-ons\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u2022 You can not slow time nor fast forward it. And no aerodynamics enhancers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2.\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:1.6;\u0022\u003EYou Can not use the flight results for it is not correct\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:1.6;\u0022\u003E\u2022 Look at the m/s at the navball instead.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:1.6;\u0022\u003E3. No Physic-less parts\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:1.6;\u0022\u003E\u2022 They could be exploited in such many ways.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:1.6;\u0022\u003E\u2022 Landing gears are allowed though.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:1.6;\u0022\u003E4. Use KSP 1.0.5\u002B\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:1.6;\u0022\u003E\u2022 1.1 is still allowed\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:1.6;\u0022\u003E5. Part mods/add-ons are allowed\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:1.6;\u0022\u003E6. Have fun\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n________________________________________\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI made the rules specifically for people who cheats, exploits and glitches the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex","CreatedById":75164,"CreatedDateTim